title: "No immediate personnel changes at this time": White House
text:
"No immediate personnel changes at this time": White House 1:10am IST - 01:20 
White House spokeswoman Sarah Sanders says President Trump is not looking to make ''immediate personnel changes at this time'' amid reports of a possible staff shake-up. Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
